-7711.jpeg">630_360_16839...</a>", "<a href="https://static.ukrinform.com/photos/2023_05/thumb_files/630_360_1683948072-6802.jpeg">630_360_16839...</a>", "<a href="https://static.ukrinform.com/photos/2023_05/thumb_files/630_360_1683948072-9954.jpeg">630_360_16839...</a>", "<a href="https://static.ukrinform.com/photos/2023_05/thumb_files/630_360_1683948074-5483.jpeg">630_360_16839...</a>", "<a href="https://static.ukrinform.com/photos/2023_05/thumb_files/630_360_1683948073-3616.jpeg">630_360_16839...</a>", "<a href="https://static.ukrinform.com/photos/2023_05/thumb_files/630_360_1683948075-8021.jpeg">630_360_16839...</a>", "<a href="https://static.ukrinform.com/photos/2023_05/thumb_files/630_360_1683948073-7820.jpeg">630_360_16839...</a>", "<a href="https://static.ukrinform.com/photos/2023_05/thumb_files/630_360_1683948075-7279.jpeg">630_360_16839...</a>", "<a href="https://static.ukrinform.com/photos/2023_05/thumb_files/630_360_1683948072-4263.jpeg">630_360_16839...</a>", "<a href="https://static.ukrinform.com/photos/2023_05/thumb_files/630_360_1683948071-9803.jpeg">630_360_16839...</a>"]</p>
